  "time_ut": 1658386082,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0db6\u0dbd\u0dc1\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0db4\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0db7\u0ddd\u0da2\u0db1\u0dba \u0d85\u0da9\u0dd4 \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0db1 \u0dbd\u0dd9\u0dc3 EU \u0d89\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dcf \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0da7\u0dd3",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The EU calls for a reduction in energy consumption",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "European Union leaders have announced a plan to reduce their dependence on Russian gas amid energy supply constraints.",
        "Accordingly, the European Commission has asked member states to reduce their energy consumption by 15% between August and the end of March.",
        "The cuts would be voluntary, but the proposals would allow the EU to make them mandatory in the event of an energy emergency."
      ],
      "title_ents": [
        {
          "text": "EU",
          "label": "ORG"
        }
      ],
